ReactJS is a java script library for building User Interfaces.
ReactJS is all about creating components.
component is a custom html element.
component is a reusable code.

React uses two libraries

1. React : for developing react component.
2. ReactDOM : for rendering react component on browser.


Q) How to create a component ?

  By extending Component class of React library.
  extending class should have render() method which returns JSX code.

  class MyComponent extends Component {
      render () {
          return (
              //JSX CODE
              <div>
                <h1>Hello React!</h1>
              </div>
          );
      }
  }


